Package: borealis
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Integrative Biology 
Version: 2020.10.07
Authors@R: person("Dave", "Angelini", email = "david.r.angelini@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for common activities in an integrative biology lab. 
    It includes tools for morphometry analysis with records of data provenance. 
    A few other functions are included for qPCR analysis, along with some sample data.
